Allah loves you and wants you to Love him too. He shows his Love by giving you anything you need,by accepting your prayers,by protecting you and by helping you. Now Show your Love to Allah (SWT) by remembering Him (dhkir).
Don’t forget that Allah says “Remember me,I will remember you”( Al-Baqara 152)
